From 8f2be8826d9436e3a5c864464f47670de9b8df3c Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Sushant Butta <sbutta@qti.qualcomm.com>
Date: Fri, 12 Sep 2025 12:09:25 +0530
Subject: [PATCH] UPSTREAM:DP:wifi:ath12k: Fix Kasan warning in amsdu padding

Currently, in ath12k_wifi7_dp_mon_pad_amsdu, the pad_start_ptr
was pointing to the end of the frag address leading to a
memory corruption of amsdu pad length.

Fix this corruption by pointing pad_start_ptr at correct address,
to add amsud padding correctly.

BUG: KASAN: use-after-free in ath12k_wifi7_dp_mon_rx_parse_ppdu_status+0x118/0x1db8
Read of size 8 at addr ffffff8004b68000 by task kworker/u10:0/35

dump_backtrace+0xd4/0xf4
show_stack+0x14/0x1c
dump_stack_lvl+0x44/0x58
print_report+0xa0/0x4ac
kasan_report+0xac/0xbc
kasan_check_range+0x1c/0x168
__asan_loadN+0x18/0x20
ath12k_wifi7_dp_mon_rx_parse_ppdu_status+0x118/0x1db8 [ath12k_wifi7]
ath12k_wifi7_dp_mon_rx_parse_ppdu_status+0x1788/0x1db8 [ath12k_wifi7]
process_scheduled_works+0x374/0x520

Patch-dependency:
	0495-04-Upstream-DP-wifi-ath12k-Support-Ethernet-packet-capt.patch

Fixes : I4966ec2a21c69736c4a6f37004f00e2db0b56d9d
	UPSTREAM:DP:wifi:ath12k: add support for ethernet packet capture in monitor mode

Signed-off-by: Sushant Butta <sbutta@qti.qualcomm.com>
---
 drivers/net/wireless/ath/ath12k/wifi7/dp_mon2.c | 4 ++++
 1 file changed, 4 insertions(+)

diff --git a/drivers/net/wireless/ath/ath12k/wifi7/dp_mon2.c b/drivers/net/wireless/ath/ath12k/wifi7/dp_mon2.c
index f9941f7..81d5818 100644
--- a/drivers/net/wireless/ath/ath12k/wifi7/dp_mon2.c
+++ b/drivers/net/wireless/ath/ath12k/wifi7/dp_mon2.c
@@ -617,6 +617,10 @@ ath12k_wifi7_dp_mon_pad_amsdu(struct ath12k_pdev_dp *dp_pdev, struct sk_buff *mp
 
 		pad_start_ptr += ath12k_wifi7_dp_mon_get_frag_size_by_idx(dp,
 									  mpdu, frag_idx);
+		/* pad_start_ptr points at end of frag, to add amsdu padding
+		 * subtract the amsdu pad len in pad_start_ptr.
+		 */
+		pad_start_ptr -= amsdu_pad;
 		memset(pad_start_ptr, 0, amsdu_pad);
 	}
 
-- 
